code: cpsr_write (CPUARMState * env , uint32_t val , uint32_t mask)
if ( ( env -> uncached_cpsr ^ val ) & mask & CPSR_M )
env -> uncached_cpsr = ( env -> uncached_cpsr & ~mask ) | ( val & mask )
env -> uncached_cpsr = ( env -> uncached_cpsr & ~mask ) | ( val & mask )
